drm/i915/pm: switch to kernel types

Mixed C99 and kernel types use is getting ugly. Prefer kernel types.

sed -i 's/\buint\(8\|16\|32\|64\)_t\b/u\1/g'

Minor checkpatch fixes sprinkled on top of the changed lines.

